query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS deterioration_curves (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  curveType ENUM('best', 'design', 'worst') NOT NULL,
  componentType VARCHAR(100),
  param1 INT NOT NULL,
  param2 INT NOT NULL,
  param3 INT NOT NULL,
  param4 INT NOT NULL,
  param5 INT NOT NULL,
  param6 INT NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  isDefault BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  interpolationType ENUM('linear', 'polynomial', 'exponential') DEFAULT 'linear',
  createdBy INT,
  projectId INT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
